VoiceFlow — WebCraftio AI Calling Platform (Phase 1)
=====================================================

A white-label AI voice calling platform for automated outbound sales calls.

ARCHITECTURE
------------
Two separate services:

1. packages/dashboard/  — Next.js 15 dashboard (deploy to Vercel free tier)
   - Dashboard UI (agents, calls, settings)
   - REST API routes
   - Telnyx/Twilio webhook receivers
   - Reads/writes Supabase

2. packages/ws-server/  — WebSocket Audio Server (deploy to Google Cloud Run)
   - Receives real-time audio from Telnyx
   - Pipes audio to Deepgram STT
   - Sends transcript to Claude Haiku
   - Sends response to ElevenLabs TTS
   - Sends audio back to Telnyx
   - Updates Supabase with results

shared/                — Shared TypeScript types

QUICK START
-----------

1. Set up Supabase:
   - Create a project at supabase.com
   - Run supabase/migrations.sql in the SQL Editor

2. Configure environment variables:
   - Copy packages/dashboard/.env.example to packages/dashboard/.env.local
   - Copy packages/ws-server/.env.example to packages/ws-server/.env
   - Fill in all API keys

3. Install dependencies:
   pnpm install

4. Run both services:
   pnpm dev

5. Deploy WebSocket server to Google Cloud Run:
   cd packages/ws-server
   gcloud run deploy voiceflow-ws-server \
     --source . --platform managed --region europe-west2 \
     --allow-unauthenticated --port 4000 \
     --min-instances 1 --max-instances 10 \
     --memory 512Mi --cpu 1 --timeout 3600

6. Deploy dashboard to Vercel:
   cd packages/dashboard
   npx vercel --prod

PROVIDERS USED
--------------
- LLM: Anthropic Claude Haiku (default) / OpenAI GPT
- STT: Deepgram Nova-3 (default) / Google STT
- TTS: ElevenLabs Flash v2.5 (default) / Deepgram TTS / Google TTS
- Telephony: Telnyx (default) / Twilio
- Database: Supabase (PostgreSQL)
- Auth: Supabase Auth

COST ESTIMATE
-------------
- Vercel dashboard: Free forever
- Supabase: Free tier forever
- Google Cloud Run: ~$8/month (covered by $300 credits ~10 months)
- Deepgram STT: $200 free credits
- ElevenLabs TTS: $5/month starter
- Telnyx calls: ~$0.007/min
- Claude Haiku: ~$0.006/call
- Total to start: ~$6/month after free tiers
